{"tid":1766243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌柒黨鐵黃衫狗/Food Panda行動","createTime":"2019-12-02T12:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T15:52:42.000Z","uid":40041,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5f5a941614d96d20d8e1c2108a47c0700ce797","tid":1766243,"uid":40041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"小弟好睇唔過眼最近黨鐵既黃衫狗，food panda明明就係打份工，唔知點解咁落力係到捉人，明明係打份最低賤既工，唔知咁落力搏咩。個d咩前線黃衫好多都係深黃真係笑話黎。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，不如我地一齊進行屌柒黃衫狗同food panda行動。好多手足可能由於交通原因所以除左黨鐵之外無其它選擇，你又可能唔夠膽跳閘又唔用綠卡。唔緊要，你可以做到一樣野，係黨鐵見到佢地既時候大家過去同佢講聲屌你老母，大大力屌又得，係耳邊細細力屌又得，得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ea5f9e13c8b7a31d3237a80d3e1dd126d690df","tid":1766243,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"[行動POST]擔心Tear Gas毒氣嘅手足，12月6號愛丁堡有「吸吸」可危集會，同我入黎推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766230</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a5f6ea3f6e0d1de3a5694f16144bcc0497f40b1d","tid":1766243,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:25:40.000Z","msg":"細細聲屌好喇，狗鐵講粗口好似要罰錢"},{"pid":"365032392a22a78e54e6cae3c0f24f8db31a8e16","tid":1766243,"uid":23135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5a5b5110164f9c8cc4be4b14b3da46cc7c1ef7c1","tid":1766243,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黨鐵職員根本同狗無分別<br />\n助紂為虐"},{"pid":"f6034ce4c96bcaa3803163e013db865837766cf0","tid":1766243,"uid":40041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}